* Create iii command line utility
Reads environment variable SIMULATION to guide its actions.
	- system
		- start: Will start the system, performing all necessary steps - done
		- stop: Will stop the system - done
		- restart: will restart the system - done
			- warm: Only deactive and reactivate nodes - done
			- cold: Will also cleanup and reconfigure nodes - done
		- boot: Launch the unbooted system - done
			--attach: Will attach to the tmux session - done
		- shutdown: will shutdown the system - done
		- attach: attach to the booted system - done
		- status: Display system information




